# Client Operations Data Cleaning & Reporting Project

## Project Overview

This project demonstrates how Python and pandas can be used to clean and report on a messy Excel dataset.

The dataset simulates a small business operations file containing client job records. The original spreadsheet included duplicate rows, missing values, inconsistent formatting, messy column names and mixed date formats.

The goal was to turn the messy spreadsheet into a clean, structured Excel file and create a simple business report with useful summary insights.
## Business Outcome

The messy dataset was reduced from 130 rows to 100 clean records, with duplicates removed, missing critical values handled, dates standardised and a multi-sheet Excel report created for business review.
